---
title: Beef & Caramelised Bacon Burger with Oven-Baked Fries
description: Sure, everyone rushes to the table when burgers are on the menu, but these ones will get them moving double-quick. That’s because we've topped each tender beef patty with a crispy piece of rasher bacon, caramelised in brown sugar – it adds a special touch and is super simple to make!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-caramelised-bacon-burger-f3ee5f9d.jpg
